# MailHog

## Installation

```bash
# sudo est facultatif

# https://github.com/mailhog/MailHog
sudo apt-get -y install golang-go
sudo go env -w GOBIN=/usr/local/bin
sudo go install github.com/mailhog/MailHog@latest

# https://github.com/mailhog/mhsendmail
sudo go install github.com/mailhog/mhsendmail@latest
```

## Lancement du serveur mail

```bash
MailHog &
```


## php.ini

```ini
# php.ini
sendmail_path = /usr/local/bin/mhsendmail
```
